<div class="thumb tright"><div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:1903-ford-rc.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b6/1903-ford-rc.jpg/180px-1903-ford-rc.jpg" decoding="async" width="180" height="133" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b6/1903-ford-rc.jpg/270px-1903-ford-rc.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b6/1903-ford-rc.jpg/360px-1903-ford-rc.jpg 2x" data-file-width="600" data-file-height="443" /></a>  <div class="thumbcaption"><div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:1903-ford-rc.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>1903 Model A</div></div></div>
